#: ../../index.rst:4
msgid "Elgg_ (:download:`pronunciation <_elgg_files/How_to_say_Elgg.mp3>`) is an open source rapid development framework for socially aware web applications. It is a great fit for building any app where users log in and share information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:8
msgid "Features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:10
msgid "**Well-documented core API** that allows developers to kick start their new project with a simple learning curve"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:11
msgid "**Composer** is the package manager of choice that greatly simplifes installation and maintenance of Elgg core and plugins"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:12
msgid "**Flexible system of hooks and events** that allows plugins to extend and modify most aspects of application's functionality and behavior"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:13
msgid "**Extendable system of views** that allows plugins to collaborate on application's presentation layer and built out complex custom themes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:14
msgid "**Cacheable system of static assets** that allows themes and plugins to serve images, stylesheets, fonts and scripts bypassing the engine"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:15
msgid "**User authentication** is powered by pluggable auth modules, which allow applications to implement custom authentication protocols"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:16
msgid "**Security** is ensured by built-in anti CSRF validation, strict XSS filters, HMAC signatures, latest cryptographic approaches to password hashing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:17
msgid "**Client-side API** powered by asynchronous JavaScript modules via RequireJS and a build-in Ajax service for easy communication with the server"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:18
msgid "**Flexible entity system** that allows applications to prototype new types of content and user interactions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:19
msgid "**Opinionated data model** with a consolidated API layer that allows the developers to easily interface with the database"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:20
msgid "**Access control system** that allows applications to build granular content access policies, as well as create private networks and intranets"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:21
msgid "**Groups** - out of the box support for user groups"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:22
msgid "**File storage** powered by flexible API that allows plugins to store user-generated files and serve/stream them without booting the engine"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:23
msgid "**Notifications service** that allows applications to subscribe users to on-site and email notifications and implement integrations with other their-party services"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:24
msgid "**RPC web services** that can be used for complex integrations with external applications and mobile clients"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:25
msgid "**Internationalization** and localization of Elgg applications is simple and can be integrated with third-party services such as Transifex"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.rst:26
msgid "**Elgg community** that can help with any arising issues and hosts a repository of **1000+ open source plugins**"
msgstr ""

